OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1772831518
OL,3,CFreight pricing and interisland ferry
OL,4,Clinks should be reviewed, say
OL,5,Cbackbenchers
OL,7,FJersey's government should review
OL,8,FDFDS's freight pricing and work with
OL,9,FGuernsey States to improve interisland
OL,10,Fconnections, according to a group of
OL,11,Fbackbench politicians.
OL,13,FAs part of a month-long review of the
OL,14,Fcontract signed between Jersey's
OL,15,Fgovernment and DFDS, a report written
OL,16,Fby the Economic and International
OL,17,FAffairs Scrutiny Panel made 21
OL,18,Frecommendations.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/11
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,385,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1772831518
OL,3,CFreight pricing and interisland ferry
OL,4,Clinks should be reviewed, say
OL,5,Cbackbenchers
OL,7,FIt includes commissioning an
OL,8,Findependent review of the flat-rate
OL,9,Ffor freight pricing, formally
OL,10,Frequesting that DFDS explore options
OL,11,Fto make journey times between Jersey
OL,12,Fand St Malo shorter, introduce a
OL,13,Ffrequent traveller discount, and
OL,14,Fcloser negotiation with politicians in
OL,15,FGuernsey over inter-island services.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/11
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,385,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1772831518
OL,3,CFreight pricing and interisland ferry
OL,4,Clinks should be reviewed, say
OL,5,Cbackbenchers
OL,7,FIt comes after it was decided in
OL,8,FNovember that a review of the
OL,9,FGovernment's agreement with DFDS would
OL,10,Fbe carried out to assess how well the
OL,11,Fprovider was meeting its contractual
OL,12,Fobligations since taking over Jersey's
OL,13,Fferry links in March last year.
OL,15,FThat move came amid growing calls from
OL,16,Fbusiness leaders for the Concession
OL,17,FAgreement signed by the two parties in
OL,18,FNovember 2024 to be assessed.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/11
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,385,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1772831518
OL,3,CFreight pricing and interisland ferry
OL,4,Clinks should be reviewed, say
OL,5,Cbackbenchers
OL,7,FDFDS has welcomed the findings and
OL,8,Fhave committed to prioritising
OL,9,F"reliable sailings, fair pricing and a
OL,10,Fbetter overall journey experience".
OL,12,FThe company recognised that the early
OL,13,Fmonths of the concession "were
OL,14,Fdifficult, following a compressed
OL,15,Fmobilisation period and the rapid
OL,16,Fintroduction of new vessels, systems
OL,17,Fand schedules".
OL,19,FThe ferry firm said its focus is now
OL,20,F"firmly on consistent delivery and
OL,21,Fbuilding confidence".
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/11
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,385,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1772831518
OL,3,CFreight pricing and interisland ferry
OL,4,Clinks should be reviewed, say
OL,5,Cbackbenchers
OL,7,FA DFDS spokesperson said: "We
OL,8,Frecognise that the first year did not
OL,9,Fmeet everyone's expectations,
OL,10,Fparticularly during the early
OL,11,Fmobilisation period.
OL,13,F"What matters is the action taken
OL,14,Fsince. We have strengthened
OL,15,Foperational planning, refined
OL,16,Ftimetables using real travel data,
OL,17,Finvested in onboard comfort and
OL,18,Faccessibility, and improved
OL,19,Fcommunication when disruption occurs.
OL,26,@oD@[OUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G5/11
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,385,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1772831518
OL,3,CFreight pricing and interisland ferry
OL,4,Clinks should be reviewed, say
OL,5,Cbackbenchers
OL,7,F"Scrutiny is an important part of
OL,8,Faccountability. Our priority for 2026
OL,9,Fis clear: reliable sailings, fair
OL,10,Fpricing and a better overall journey
OL,11,Fexperience."
OL,13,FDFDS also said 2026 would be a year of
OL,14,Fconsolidation, embedding improvements,
OL,15,Fand making services easier to plan for
OL,16,Fislanders, visitors and freight
OL,17,Fcustomers.
OL,19,FOther key DFDS changes include:
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@LO]
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G6/11
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,385,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1772831518
OL,3,CFreight pricing and interisland ferry
OL,4,Clinks should be reviewed, say
OL,5,Cbackbenchers
OL,7,FThe company also highlighted its
OL,8,Frecently announced 15% 'Islander
OL,9,FSpecial Discount' and said it is
OL,10,Fworking to ensure pricing is
OL,11,F"straightforward and transparent at
OL,12,Fthe point of booking".
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G7/11
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,385,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1772831518
OL,3,CFreight pricing and interisland ferry
OL,4,Clinks should be reviewed, say
OL,5,Cbackbenchers
OL,7,FFollowing the report's publication,
OL,8,FDeputy Montfort Tadier, Chair of the
OL,9,FPanel, said: "It is clear that the
OL,10,Fservice islanders and businesses are
OL,11,Fexperiencing does not match the
OL,12,Fexpectations they may have had, and
OL,13,Fthis has resulted in much public
OL,14,Fcommentary about the slow sailing
OL,15,Ftimes, lack of day trips to St. Malo,
OL,16,Fcondition of the vessels and prices.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G8/11
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,385,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38409
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1772831518
OL,3,CFreight pricing and interisland ferry
OL,4,Clinks should be reviewed, say
OL,5,Cbackbenchers
OL,7,F"Local businesses and retailers have
OL,8,Falso been critical of the flat-rate
OL,9,Ffreight prices that were introduced as
OL,10,Fpart of the contract. This review has
OL,11,Fhighlighted that, while some of the
OL,12,Fearly problems can be attributed to
OL,13,Fthe short lead-in time DFDS faced due
OL,14,Fto the tender process, others are as a
OL,15,Fdirect result of the Concession
OL,16,FAgreement.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G9/11
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,385,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38410
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1772831518
OL,3,CFreight pricing and interisland ferry
OL,4,Clinks should be reviewed, say
OL,5,Cbackbenchers
OL,7,F"The Panel has found that some areas
OL,8,Fof the contract do not contain
OL,9,Fconcrete requirements which can lead
OL,10,Fto differences in how they are
OL,11,Finterpreted by each party.
OL,13,F"While it is not possible at this
OL,14,Fstage for the contract to be
OL,15,Frenegotiated, there are mechanisms
OL,16,Favailable that the Minister can use to
OL,17,Frequest variations, and we strongly
OL,18,Frecommend that he use them to address
OL,19,Fthe concerns raised.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws        G10/11
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,385,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38411
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1772831518
OL,3,CFreight pricing and interisland ferry
OL,4,Clinks should be reviewed, say
OL,5,Cbackbenchers
OL,7,F"As this is an interim report, we will
OL,8,Fbe suggesting that the next Panel
OL,9,Fcarry out a further review of the
OL,10,Fservice once sufficient time has
OL,11,Fpassed to allow for comparisons to be
OL,12,Fmade."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws        G11/11
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
